国博士生的专业课「没必要」？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b06fd7b7ca72c777ef6085d136712e5c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "94 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/460069147"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IoaP24fepg/9zEAMaCDY0NTE3NTA3IOvGjIUGMAM4pAJAJHIJNDYwMDY5MTQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1621415553.9919362", "card_id": "Q_458442399", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 88}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "520 学生党适合送给女朋友的礼物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9a9c3ff3601319553ee8a3378861b444_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "89 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458442399"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IoaP24fepg/9zEAMaCDY0MTU2NDkzIN/s2oQGMAM4gwFAJXIJNDU4NDQyMzk5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1621415553.992316", "card_id": "Q_320387789", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 490}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "男生最忘不了什么样的女生？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a0110ac65b494362f90be6d323bd70c6_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/320387789"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IoaP24fepg/9zEAMaCDMzNDczMjIzIKak1uUFMGU4whhAJnIJMzIwMzg3Nzg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1621415553.992797", "card_id": "Q_423618604", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 690}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你玩《英雄联盟》收到过的最高评价是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-c67225d82843fad033770e1863